arStrings.szText: We'll see how well Artair's magic works. Me, I prefer a more direct deterrent even goatmen can understand.
Phelan is friendlier as the player is helping out
Ahh, the damned beasts have moved into the Pits at the south end of the Downs. They're led by some big ugly brute of a thing named Blackhorn.
(spits) Mounting that bastard's head on a pole would teach them what happens to those that attack the Downs.
